title: Eddie Brings Back 'Walk' Gifts! + Brad Paisley And Jimmie Allen Perform In Studio + Fun Fact Friday Face-Off: Amy vs. Scuba Steve
itunes:title: Eddie Brings Back 'Walk' Gifts! + Brad Paisley And Jimmie Allen Perform In Studio + Fun Fact Friday Face-Off: Amy vs. Scuba Steve
description:
Eddie is back in the studio today! He brought us all a gift back he got from his walk from West Virginia down to Tennessee. Brad Paisley and Jimmie Allen are in as the Friday Morning Conversation and the perform one of Jimmie’s songs together. Scuba Steve tries to take down the Queen of Facts, Amy!
